description: The main compartment zipper extends all the way to the bottom of the pack, so it can be fully opened even while it's hanging. A built-in padded laptop sleeve, a mesh side water bottle pocket, a small item storage pouch and a generously-sized main storage compartments offer plenty of room for kids' stuff. Durable denier polyester with reinforced stitching lasts all year. *ACCO Brands will replace any Five Star Sidekick Plus Backpack that is returned within one year from the date of purchase. The guarantee does not cover damage due to abuse. Contact ACCO Brands Consumer Affairs at www.mead.com for instructions.
title: Five Star Backpack Sidekick, Holds 16 Inch Laptop, Blue (72388)
